        <heading>Tobacco Products</heading>
        <section eId="sec_59_14_504">
          <num>59-14-504</num>
          <heading>Responsibility for placement of warning labels -- One label required.</heading>
          <content>
            <p>59-14-504.
Responsibility for placement of warning labels -- One label required.
It is the intent and purpose of this part to require all manufacturers, jobbers, wholesalers, and distributors to securely affix the warning labels required by Section
59-14-501
.  When warning labels are affixed as required by this part, no additional warning label is required, regardless of how often the articles are sold or resold in the state.
Renumbered and Amended by Chapter
2
, 1987 General Session</p>
